-YOU OWE ME, COWBOY.

16:14.886 --> 16:17.759
-I THINK YOU'RE FORGETTING
THIS IS BETTER THAN JAIL.

16:17.889 --> 16:20.457
-THIS WILL MAKE US EVEN.

16:20.588 --> 16:24.374
[INTENSE MUSIC]

16:35.907 --> 16:37.213
-ALRIGHT, ALRIGHT.

16:37.344 --> 16:38.998
ONE SHOT FOR THE
HISTORY BOOKS HERE.

16:41.348 --> 16:42.218
SAY CHEESE.

