17:23.085 --> 17:25.000
-ALRIGHT, LET'S GET ON.

17:26.784 --> 17:28.569
-WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU, MAN?

17:28.699 --> 17:30.005
-WHAT ARE YOU WAITING
FOR? MOVE, MOVE!

17:30.136 --> 17:32.138
-HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

17:32.268 --> 17:34.879
