31:47.166 --> 31:50.778
[INTENSE MUSIC]

34:02.431 --> 34:03.737
-AGH!

34:03.867 --> 34:05.043
AH!

34:06.044 --> 34:08.871
[FIGHTING, GRUNTING]

34:09.003 --> 34:10.831
-AH!

34:12.179 --> 34:14.530
-WHAT, WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

34:14.661 --> 34:16.054
-WHAT, ARE YOU STUPID?

34:16.184 --> 34:17.793
I WAS GETTING SOME
SPENDING MONEY.

34:18.969 --> 34:20.362
-I AIN'T TALKING
ABOUT THE MONEY, MAN.

34:20.971 --> 34:22.668
I'M TALKING ABOUT
YOU SPITTING ON ME.

34:22.799 --> 34:24.844
[GRUNTING]

34:24.975 --> 34:27.500
OH, YOU'RE SO TOUGH,
AREN'T YOU, HUH?

34:27.630 --> 34:29.893
TOO TOUGH FOR ME, TOO
TOUGH FOR MY WATER PROGRAM.

34:32.025 --> 34:34.376
YOU THINK YOU'RE AS
TOUGH AS YOUR OLD MAN,

34:34.507 --> 34:36.422
BUT YOU AIN'T TOUGH ENOUGH
TO STAND UP TO HIM, ARE YOU?

34:37.292 --> 34:38.119
-WOULD YOU BE?

34:40.730 --> 34:42.123
-NO. NO.

34:43.168 --> 34:44.429
YOU'RE RIGHT.

34:47.694 --> 34:50.784
HERE, MAN, TAKE IT. TAKE
THE MONEY. IT'S MINE.

34:52.045 --> 34:53.525
TELL YOUR OLD MAN YOU STOLE IT.

34:59.880 --> 35:01.490
-HE'S ALL I GOT, MAN.

35:01.621 --> 35:03.884
-NO. NO, HE'S NOT, MAN.

35:04.014 --> 35:05.842
THAT'S WHAT I'M
TRYING TO TELL YOU.

35:05.973 --> 35:08.671
THERE'S OTHER PEOPLE,
THERE'S OTHER WAYS, MAN.

