HELL, I FOUND ONE.

35:10.673 --> 35:13.589
I'M NOT SAYING MINE'S THE
WAY, BUT TAKE A CHANCE, MAN.

35:13.720 --> 35:15.113
TRY TO FIND ONE FOR YOURSELF.

35:15.243 --> 35:16.636
-HOW?

35:20.770 --> 35:21.684
-LET ME HELP YOU.

35:24.687 --> 35:26.167
OH COME ON, MAN.

35:26.298 --> 35:28.343
YOU'VE BEEN BEATEN UP
BY, BY BOOGIE BOARDS,

35:29.301 --> 35:31.172
BASHED BY WAVES.

35:33.218 --> 35:35.742
HOLDING OUT YOUR HAND
SHOULDN'T BE TOO HARD

35:35.872 --> 35:37.439
A TOUGH GUY LIKE YOU

35:38.048 --> 35:40.138
COME ON, MAN, LET ME HELP.

35:41.400 --> 35:42.749
COME ON.

35:47.319 --> 35:51.149
[MELLOW MUSIC]

35:59.374 --> 36:03.161
[MELLOW MUSIC]

36:10.211 --> 36:11.647
WHAT'S THAT?

36:11.778 --> 36:13.823
-HEY. IT'S A COURSE
CATALOG FOR SEPTEMBER.

36:13.954 --> 36:17.653
OH, MY GOD. OH, CORT COMES
INTO TOWN, AND YOU GET CREAMED.

36:17.784 --> 36:19.220
-WELL, AT LEAST YOU'RE
HERE TO TAKE CARE OF ME.

36:19.351 --> 36:20.613
-OH.

36:22.528 --> 36:25.183
-MAYBE I OUGHT TO HAVE
JOHN D. CORT STICK AROUND.

36:25.748 --> 36:27.228
-AS IF HE WOULD.

36:27.359 --> 36:29.709
-HEY, I DON'T KNOW,
HE MIGHT SURPRISE US.

36:29.839 --> 36:31.276
AFTER ALL, HE'S BEEN
A BIG HERO THIS WEEK.

36:31.406 --> 36:32.364
-HE'S ALWAYS BEEN
YOUR BIG HERO.

36:32.494 --> 36:35.149
-NOW, THAT'S NOT FAIR.

36:35.280 --> 36:36.803
NOW COME ON, I'M NOT
GOING TO TURN INTO

36:37.543 --> 36:39.197
JOHN D. CORT AND
RUN OUT ON YOU.

36:40.328 --> 36:42.939
HE ENVIES ME. YOU KNOW WHY?

36:43.897 --> 36:45.072
BECAUSE I HAVE YOU.

36:45.203 --> 36:46.334
-MMM.

36:46.465 --> 36:47.857
-AND IT'S TRUE.

36:49.381 --> 36:50.904
[KISSING]

36:51.034 --> 36:52.166
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHERE
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE GOING?

36:52.297 --> 36:54.037
-I AM GOING TO GET
YOU AN ICE PACK.

36:56.562 --> 36:57.519
-OH.

36:58.520 --> 36:59.782
FINE.

37:00.522 --> 37:01.784
[LAUGHING]

37:01.915 --> 37:03.482
-I THINK WE GOT THE HANG OF IT.

37:04.047 --> 37:06.354
-HOMES, HOMES.
LOOK AT ME. [LAUGHING]

37:06.485 --> 37:07.486
-WATCH OUT!

37:07.616 --> 37:11.011
[LAUGHING]

37:11.141 --> 37:12.882
YOU'RE DOING GOOD.

37:14.710 --> 37:16.538
-HOW IS IT GOING OUT THERE?

37:16.669 --> 37:19.149
I MEAN, BESIDES THE FACT THAT
EDDIE LOOKS LIKE AN EGGPLANT.

37:19.280 --> 37:21.761
-CONSIDERING ALL THEY'VE
BEEN THROUGH? GREAT.

37:22.588 --> 37:23.589
-MAN: WATCH IT!

37:23.719 --> 37:24.720
-GET AWAY FROM ME WITH THAT.

37:24.851 --> 37:26.244
THAT THING WON'T HAPPEN TO ME.

37:30.944 --> 37:34.339
-YOU COULD CALL THIS
THEIR FAREWELL VOYAGE.

37:35.122 --> 37:36.036
-WHOO!

37:36.166 --> 37:37.646
[SPLASHING]

37:37.777 --> 37:39.431
[LAUGHING, SPLASHING]

37:41.868 --> 37:45.263
[SPLASHES AND LAUGHING]

37:54.446 --> 37:57.666
-MEMO! COME ON! I WANT YOU!

37:59.842 --> 38:01.061
I WANT YOU NOW!

38:01.191 --> 38:02.018
-LISTEN.

38:02.149 --> 38:03.759
-WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

38:03.890 --> 38:04.543
-COME ON, DON'T,
YOU'RE EMBARRASSING ME.

38:04.673 --> 38:05.718
-YOU SNUCK OUT ON ME!

38:05.848 --> 38:06.849
-LET'S GO HOME. NOT HERE, MAN.

38:06.980 --> 38:08.068
-DON'T TALK BACK TO ME!

38:08.198 --> 38:09.417
-COME ON, DAD! I'M
TRYING TO TALK TO YOU.

38:09.548 --> 38:10.636
-COME HOME WITH ME RIGHT NOW!

38:10.766 --> 38:11.898
-NO!

38:13.247 --> 38:14.727
[SPLASH]

38:14.857 --> 38:17.207
[SHOUTING IN SPANISH]

38:17.338 --> 38:19.122
-HEY,
HE'S NOT COMING UP.

38:19.253 --> 38:20.646
-HE'S GOT TO, MAN!

38:20.776 --> 38:21.734
-HE CAN'T SWIM.

38:24.258 --> 38:26.173
-HEY,
HE CAN'T SWIM, MAN.

38:30.003 --> 38:30.917
-OH, MAN,
HE'S SINKING LIKE...

38:35.965 --> 38:36.836
-WHERE IS HE?

38:36.966 --> 38:39.273
-I DON'T KNOW, MAN.

38:39.404 --> 38:43.756
[INTENSE MUSIC]

39:03.776 --> 39:05.081
IS HE ALL RIGHT?

39:06.909 --> 39:09.956
-OVER HERE, GET HIM AROUND,
GET HIM AROUND, GIVE HIM ROOM.

39:23.230 --> 39:24.623
-EDDIE: ALRIGHT, READY?

39:24.753 --> 39:27.408
-ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR,
FIVE. COME ON, POP.

39:27.539 --> 39:28.409
-I'LL TAKE OVER NOW.
-ONE, TWO, THREE--

39:28.540 --> 39:29.584
-LET HIM BE, LET HIM BE.

39:30.193 --> 39:31.325
-FOUR, FIVE. COME ON, POP.

39:32.065 --> 39:35.068
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

39:35.198 --> 39:38.288
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

39:39.028 --> 39:41.770
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

39:41.901 --> 39:44.294
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

39:45.600 --> 39:46.993
COME ON, DAD.

39:47.123 --> 39:49.430
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR...

39:49.561 --> 39:51.693
[COUGHING]

39:52.433 --> 39:53.739
POP.

39:54.348 --> 39:55.784
-MIJO, MIJO.

40:11.757 --> 40:12.714
-LATER.

40:13.541 --> 40:14.803
-THANKS A LOT.

40:17.066 --> 40:18.285
-TAKE CARE, HOMES.

40:18.416 --> 40:19.895
[CAR ENGINE STARTING]

40:21.419 --> 40:23.595
-WELL, I'D SAY IT'S WORKING.

40:24.422 --> 40:25.901
-BUT IS IT ENOUGH?

40:26.032 --> 40:29.252
-WELL, LET ME ASK YOU,
IS ANYTHING EVER ENOUGH?

40:30.036 --> 40:32.255
-MAYBE. I, I DON'T KNOW.

40:32.386 --> 40:35.302
I JUST WISH THAT WE COULD
KEEP A GUY LIKE MEMO

40:35.433 --> 40:37.347
AROUND HERE FOR MORE
THAN A WEEK AT A TIME.

40:37.478 --> 40:39.872
I'D BE HAPPY IF IT
WAS FOR A MONTH.

40:40.002 --> 40:41.787
-WELL, YOU KNOW, MAYBE HE, UM,

40:41.917 --> 40:43.179
MAYBE HE OUGHT TO COME WITH ME.

40:43.310 --> 40:45.138
-YEAH, RIGHT. TO THE CARIBBEAN?

40:45.268 --> 40:47.314
TO SAIL THE SOUTH SEAS?
-I'M SERIOUS.

40:47.445 --> 40:48.315
I'M ALMOST SETTLING DOWN.

40:48.446 --> 40:49.838
-AH, LET ME GUESS.

40:49.969 --> 40:51.492
THE OPERATIVE WORD
HERE IS ALMOST, RIGHT?

40:52.537 --> 40:53.842
-YOU EVER HEAR
OF OUTWARD BOUND?

40:54.887 --> 40:57.324
-YEAH, YEAH. ISN'T THAT
WHERE YOU TAKE THE KIDS

40:57.455 --> 40:59.326
TO THE MOUNTAINS AND THEY
LEARN ABOUT SURVIVAL?

40:59.457 --> 41:01.154
-AND ABOUT THEMSELVES.

41:01.284 --> 41:02.808
I'M GOING TO BE RUNNING
IT UP NEAR IDYLLWILD.

41:02.938 --> 41:05.201
IT'S FOR KIDS LIKE
MEMO AND FOR ME.

41:06.072 --> 41:08.422
I DON'T KNOW THOUGH,
A YEAR IN ONE PLACE

41:08.553 --> 41:10.293
I MIGHT GET A LITTLE TWITCHY.

41:10.424 --> 41:11.860
[LAUGHS]

41:11.991 --> 41:13.035
-I DON'T KNOW, CORT,
I THINK THERE MIGHT BE

41:13.166 --> 41:13.993
SOME HOPE FOR YOU YET.

41:14.123 --> 41:15.473
-THANK YOU.

41:17.083 --> 41:19.433
HEY, WHAT DO YOU SAY WE JUMP
ON THE BIKES AND HEAD DOWNTOWN.

41:20.086 --> 41:21.261
ASSASSIN ARGIRO VERSUS

41:21.391 --> 41:22.741
-CORT, EDDIE: SLUGGER SANCHEZ?

41:22.871 --> 41:23.785
-CORT: YOU GOT IT.

41:23.916 --> 41:26.571
-TEMPTING, VERY TEMPTING,

41:27.833 --> 41:29.269
BUT I DON'T THINK SO.

41:29.399 --> 41:30.662
I THINK I WANT TO
SPEND THE EVENING

41:30.792 --> 41:32.228
WITH MY FAVORITE SLUGGER.

41:32.359 --> 41:34.404
-WELL, I DON'T BLAME YOU.

41:36.798 --> 41:40.498
HEY HEY, I ALMOST
FORGOT. LET ME SEE HERE.

41:41.455 --> 41:42.369
HMM.

41:43.152 --> 41:44.458
THOSE ARE FOR YOU.

41:45.067 --> 41:46.112
-THANKS.

41:48.680 --> 41:52.597
[MELLOW MUSIC]

41:55.643 --> 41:57.123
[KISSING]

41:57.950 --> 42:02.824
[MELLOW MUSIC]

42:08.743 --> 42:12.791
[END THEME PLAYING]
